/news/music/kiss-of-life-sticky-single-music-video-release-3769091">生活的亲吻与他们的新单曲“粘性”和夏季音乐录影带卷土重来</a>。这首歌伴随着一个B面，“ Te Quiero”。</p><p>该帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-dk-cover-day6-happy-3770988">收听了17个DK Cover Day的“ Happy”的“ Happy”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
